title: Wrapping Gen Q
itunes:title: Wrapping Gen Q
description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

Edited by Diane Kang


Leisha teases a couple special cameos in the new season of THE L WORD: GENERATION Q, Kate feels like she’s walking through tar sometimes. Then they’re graced by Kate’s wife, Ana, who wishes to defend herself and her love of rules.
